SIMPLE: mindless
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Mindless
<hw>Mind"less</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Not indued with mind
or intellectual powers; stupid; unthinking.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Unmindful; inattentive; heedless;
careless.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Cursed Athens, <qex>mindless</qex> of thy worth.</q>
<rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Mine</ent>⟦br⟧
